name: Sunset In Paradise
description:
I would often travel in my mind, looking through imagined windows to see floods of colors, and beautiful sunsets. They might have said my head was in the clouds, but it was my sanctuary. 14 years of separation from all I loved in the world until I won relief and release in 2018. I lived in a cold gray world, yet painted with explosive colors that remain vivid relief to this day.
